{"tid":1488662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[檢討] Twitter 文宣撚入 我覺得我地用錯撚晒方法","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T00:38:24.000Z","uid":218313,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1d01a1530acfac233ba25ab204df0bba1d3e670a","tid":1488662,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:24:12.000Z","msg":"今晚有巴打發起Twitter 推<span style=\"color: orange;\">攬炒巴</span>賣報紙廣告單野<br />\n但好多巴絲都無用開<span style=\"color: blue;\">Twitter</span> (小弟都係), <span style=\"color: red;\">攪到成件事變得好膠</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題如下:<br />\n<br />\n1&gt; 好多人用同一個hashtag share 同一張相, 無原創性, 成板都係同一樣野...<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根本就係SPAM</span> <br />\n<br />\n2&gt; <ins>求其打兩隻字</ins>, e.g plz help us ,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貼張相就Tweet 出去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3&gt; Tag 某D 記者, 百9 幾人TAG 佢我諗佢會覺得好煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得如果要做職業<del>五毛</del>文宣, 最少要:<br />\n<br />\n1&gt; 當自己係記者,<span style=\"color: orange;\"> 最少都打一小段野</span>, Twitter 唔係instagram, 唔係只係睇相<br />\n2&gt; 係咪集中like 或者retweet 同一個post 好d? 加一個特別hashtag 等同路人搵到個post?<br />\n<br />\n我都係Twitter 新仔, 學緊野, 有錯請指教"},{"pid":"c936f439709efcfc58ec26b54643ff8b414a74be","tid":1488662,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_